          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter is in Little Flower Nursery. The teachers are well experienced and approachable. Alongwith the activities, the teachers also help in inculcating daily good habits and manners. They make sure that the parent is aware of what was taught in class on a daily basis. My daughter loves going to her school everyday and she often talks about her teachers - Miss Eileen and Miss Gurmeet. Overall - good school and good teachers. Would highly recommend this school for nursery.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
