            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter is in Nursery. It's wonderful seeing our daughter get excited about going to school here. The teachers really make an effort to engage the kids and develop them in a very individualized way. The management is really committed to providing a safe, fun, and loving environment. Great school, great teachers and support. My daughter has made brilliant progress. My daughter loves school and Ms.Eileen she always talks about her teaching and learning at home. I want to thank you for the efforts that you take for the betterment of the kids at the school are worth appreciation.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
